		background: white;
		text-indent: 11px;
	}

	#over {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		opacity: 0.8; /*设置背景色透明度,1为完全不透明,IE需要使用filter:alpha(opacity=80);*/
		filter: alpha(opacity=80);
		display: none;
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		z-index: 1;
		background: silver;
	}
